a_{\\rm peak}$) and the jet power ($P_{\\rm jet}$), which is\nconsistent with the blazar sequence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2020 16:14:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-17"}
