h rate of pancreatic cancers and the speed with which\nevolution occurs in reality. Despite this, we find that the frequency of\nresistant mutants is far too high to be explained without resorting to novel\nmechanisms of cross-resistance to multiple drugs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2020 17:15:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-20"}
