duce sufficiently high\ncovering fractions of extended, cold gas as observed to surround massive\ngalaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2020 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2020 15:12:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-09"}
